valid (**Telegram channel = OK**), but gateway doctor reports this warning:\n\n- `channels.telegram.groupPolicy = \"allowlist\"`\n- `groupAllowFrom` is empty  \nвһЎпёҸ so **group messages are being silently dropped**.\n\nThat usually feels like вҖңbot not working,вҖқ especially in group chats.\n\n### Quick fix options\n1. **Open groups to everyone**  \n   Set `groupPolicy` to `\"open\"`.\n\n2. **Keep allowlist mode (safer)**  \n   Add your Telegram user ID(s) to `channels.telegram.groupAllowFrom` (or `allowFrom`).\n\nIf you want, I can help you patch the config nowвҖ”just tell me whether you want **open** or **allowlist** behavior.  \nAlso: if your bot fails in **DM too**, say that, and IвҖҷll run the next checks immediately.","textSignature":"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8b34bd2388193ac1dccbfaaba3230"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":483,"output":286,"cacheRead":11264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12033,"cost":{"input":0.00084525,"output":0.004004,"cacheRead":0.0019711999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006820449999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772663625574}}
