CDEF1234567890/getMe\n```\n\nIf token is bad, you should get **401 Unauthorized**, not 404.\n\nGiven your OpenClaw status showed Telegram **State: OK**, your token is probably fine.  \nWant me to give you a one-line PowerShell command that tests it safely from terminal?","textSignature":"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8b3c8daa08193a32c7aed65e14f6e"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":356,"output":225,"cacheRead":12032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12613,"cost":{"input":0.000623,"output":0.00315,"cacheRead":0.0021056,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0058785999999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772663751288}}
