teway stop\n```\n\nThen on **this desktop** confirm main is healthy:\n\n```powershell\nopenclaw status\n```\n\nIf you paste both outputs, IвҖҷll confirm the switch is complete.","textSignature":"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8bbedda408193b3dab322596f33dc"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":442,"output":183,"cacheRead":28544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29169,"cost":{"input":0.0007735,"output":0.002562,"cacheRead":0.0049952,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0083307}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772665835683}}
