вҖқ\nPick one of these:\n\n1. **Git repo sync** (best for configs/docs/code)\n   - Commit/push on main, pull on other machine.\n2. **Cloud folder sync** (Google Drive/OneDrive/Dropbox)\n   - Put shared files in synced folder.\n3. **Scheduled backup/rsync job**\n   - Periodic copy from main вҶ’ second machine.\n\n### Recommended for your setup\n- Keep this desktop as **source of truth (main)**.\n- Sync only key paths (not whole system blindly), e.g.:\n  - `C:\\Users\\tonyb\\.openclaw\\workspace`\n  - optionally selected `.openclaw` config/state files\n\nIf you want, I can give you the exact step-by-step for **OneDrive sync** or **Git sync** right now (your choice).","textSignature":"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8bcbf245c8193b58ee082643be1b9"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":194,"output":298,"cacheRead":30208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30700,"cost":{"input":0.0003395,"output":0.004172,"cacheRead":0.0052864,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.009797900000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772666045135}}
