atus\n- It is **not fully complete yet**.\n- Monitor log is stuck at: `src(22/25) drive(21/24)` for a while.\n- That means Google Drive is still missing one item compared to local source.\n- Since your **laptop is offline**, it canвҖҷt receive updates anyway right now.\n\n### Telegram status\nI checked live status just now:\n- **Telegram channel = ON / OK**\n- Bot auth is healthy on this desktop\n\nSo Telegram isnвҖҷt down globally.  \nIf itвҖҷs вҖңfailing,вҖқ itвҖҷs likely one of these:\n1. YouвҖҷre testing in a **group** (your config is `groupPolicy: allowlist`, so groups are blocked unless allowed)\n2. Message routing delay or wrong chat/thread\n3. Temporary client-side issue\n\nYour current Telegram config:\n- DMs: `open` вң…\n- Groups: `allowlist` (restricted) вҡ пёҸ\n\nIf you tell me **where** itвҖҷs failing (DM vs group), IвҖҷll fix that exact path immediately.","textSignature":"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8d32d9f7c8193b19251c906e811d3"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":1491,"output":334,"cacheRead":41728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43553,"cost":{"input":0.00260925,"output":0.004676,"cacheRead":0.0073024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01458765}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772671778764}}
