t вҖ” **5327 means you measured a different/larger tree**, not the mirrored target we expected.\n\nLetвҖҷs force the exact check + clean mirror on laptop:\n\n```powershell\n$src = \"G:\\My Drive\\openclaw-workspace-main\"\n$dst = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\"\n\n# sanity check paths\nTest-Path $src\nTest-Path $dst\n\n# clean mirror (exact)\nrobocopy $src $dst /MIR /R:1 /W:1\n\n# exact counts\n(Get-ChildItem $src -Recurse -Force | Measure-Object).Count\n(Get-ChildItem $dst -Recurse -Force | Measure-Object).Count\n```\n\nYou should see the **same number for src and dst** (currently should be around 25).  \nIf you paste those last two numbers, IвҖҷll confirm immediately.","textSignature":"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8d94d8f148193b49a804a237d4669"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":196,"output":300,"cacheRead":44928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45424,"cost":{"input":0.000343,"output":0.0042,"cacheRead":0.0078624,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0124054}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772673351298}}
