e data/workflows outside `workspace`\n\nSo if you mean **вҖңeverything including agents/workflows/stateвҖқ**, answer is **no, not automatically**.\n\nIf you want true full clone, we need to sync/copy these too:\n- `C:\\Users\\tonyb\\.openclaw\\agents\\`\n- `C:\\Users\\tonyb\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json`\n- any other required `.openclaw` config/state paths\n\nIf you want, IвҖҷll give you one safe вҖңfull profile mirrorвҖқ command set next.","textSignature":"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8db41cd4c8193b81145279fa25979"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":297,"output":248,"cacheRead":45056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45601,"cost":{"input":0.00051975,"output":0.003472,"cacheRead":0.007884799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01187655}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772673853445}}
