\"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Checking service and gateway status**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_ksZ8IxSpSOPIvjcmHdlOA26j|fc_016894fb01b951d60169a8d2f167d08193a888cc45228603b8\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"openclaw status --deep\",\n            \"workdir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\",\n            \"yieldMs\": 120000\n          },\n          \"partialJson\": \"{\\\"command\\\":\\\"openclaw status --deep\\\",\\\"workdir\\\":\\\"C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\tonyb\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\\workspace\\\",\\\"yieldMs\\\":120000}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772671712584\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Diagnosing Telegram message delivery issues**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_CzG5eehExA0OBgG3xXldrsF2|fc_016894fb01b951d60169a8d31b52a88193aba63e88929f8b14\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"openclaw config get channels.telegram\",\n            \"workdir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\"\n          },\n          \"partialJson\": \"{\\\"command\\\":\\\"openclaw config get channels.telegram\\\",\\\"workdir\\\":\\\"C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\tonyb\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\\workspace\\\"}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772671743307\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Explaining sync mismatch and Telegram issues**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \" HereвҖҷs where weвҖҷre at right now:\\n\\n### Sync status\\n- It is **not fully complete yet**.\\n- Monitor log is stuck at: `src(22/25) drive(21/24)` for a while.\\n- That means Google Drive is still missing one item compared to local source.\\n- Since your **laptop is offline**, it canвҖҷt receive updates anyway right now.\\n\\n### Telegram status\\nI checked live status just now:\\n- **Telegram channel = ON / OK**\\n- Bot auth is healthy on this desktop\\n\\nSo Telegram isnвҖҷt down globally.  \\nIf itвҖҷs вҖңfailing,вҖқ itвҖҷs likely one of these:\\n1. YouвҖҷre testing in a **group** (your config is `groupPolicy: allowlist`, so groups are blocked unless allowed)\\n2. Message routing delay or wrong chat/thread\\n3. Temporary client-side issue\\n\\nYour current Telegram config:\\n- DMs: `open` вң…\\n- Groups: `allowlist` (restricted) вҡ пёҸ\\n\\nIf you tell me **where** itвҖҷs failing (DM vs group), IвҖҷll fix that exact path immediately.\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8d32d9f7c8193b19251c906e811d3\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772671778764\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"can we get finishe\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1772671870194\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Preparing sync status check**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_ETz2JIDDmQrQ4ZxPwshSLnPy|fc_016894fb01b951d60169a8d38f04c881938fca845eb9903d72\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\