bocopy \\\"G:\\\\My Drive\\\\openclaw-workspace-main\\\" \\\"$env:USERPROFILE\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\" /MIR /R:1 /W:1\\n```\\n\\nThen verify on laptop:\\n\\n```powershell\\nGet-ChildItem \\\"$env:USERPROFILE\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\" -Recurse -Force | Measure-Object\\n```\\n\\nIf it shows **25**, youвҖҷre fully finished on both machines.\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8d3c7f9688193b47d98f1a434914b\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772671932630\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"are we woking\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1772672532511\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \" Yes вҖ” weвҖҷre working.\\n\\nCurrent state:\\n- **Desktop main:** working\\n- **Telegram:** ON/OK\\n- **Desktop вҶ” Google Drive sync:** matched (25/25)\\n\\nOnly pending piece:\\n- Laptop is offline, so final mirror to laptop waits until itвҖҷs back on.\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8d61ebe488193b306ed1fa31bed7e\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772672532524\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"can we get to te laptop now\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1772672563691\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Checking node status**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_6yTlpxSujZV0ZqAyFMxHjqy1|fc_016894fb01b951d60169a8d63a00788193bd81fe6b71c49775\",\n          \"name\": \"nodes\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"action\": \"status\"\n          },\n          \"partialJson\": \"{\\\"action\\\":\\\"status\\\"}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772672563694\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \" Not yet вҖ” I still canвҖҷt reach it from here.\\n\\nI checked and there are **no active nodes connected** right now, so your laptop is still effectively offline to me.\\n\\nWhen the laptop is back on:\\n1. connect it to internet  \\n2. start OpenClaw  \\n3. tell me вҖңlaptop onlineвҖқ  \\n\\nIвҖҷll immediately verify connection and run the final mirror step.\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8d642150881938b5c44cbd6b2ba33\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772672571305\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"laptop is up and doing final sync pariy\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1772672644355\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Checking node and device status**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_DtXFGu8SyfgDsLWIVhnTah70|fc_016894fb01b951d60169a8d68ceff08193b254600908a4e34f\",\n          \"name\": \"nodes\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"action\": \"status\"\n          },\n          \"partialJson\": \"{\\\"action\\\":\\\"status\\\"}\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_5OrV9Zvw4R1mnri1AwBEfkhS|fc_016894fb01b951d60169a8d68cf004819397df2697f63d5a26\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"openclaw devices list\",\n            \"workdir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\"\n          },\n          \"partialJson\": \"{\\\"command\\\":\\\"openclaw devices list\\\",\\\"workdir\\\":\\\"C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\tonyb\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\\workspace\\\"}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772672644360\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Assessing robocopy sync status**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \" Nice вҖ” that lines up.\\n\\nI just checked:\\n- **Devices paired: 2** вң…\\n- **No active node session yet** (`nodes: []`) вҖ” thatвҖҷs okay for file parity.\\n\\nFor final parity on the **laptop**, run:\\n\\n```powershell\\nrobocopy \\\"G:\\\\My Drive\\\\openclaw-workspace-main\\\" \\\"$env:USERPROFILE\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\" /MIR /R:1 /W:1\\nGet-ChildItem \\\"$env:USERPROFILE\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\" -Recurse -Force | Measure-Object\\n```\\n\\nTarget count should be **25**.  \\nSend me the laptop count and IвҖҷll confirm weвҖҷre fully done.\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8d69565548193ac9c749dce249dd3\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772672657889\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"where are we at moving files\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1772673301769\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \" Quick status:\\n\\n- **Desktop вҶ’ Google Drive:** complete (matched **25/25**) вң…\\n- **Laptop:** pending final mirror verification вҸі\\n- **Telegram/main setup:** working on desktop вң…\\n\\nSo weвҖҷre at the last step: run the mirror on laptop and confirm recurse count = **25**.  \\nOnce you send that count, we can call file migration done.\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8d917d10c8193b4ae32fb4c8cc95a\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772673301774\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Count : 5327 that was the count\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1772673351293\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Clarifying sync scope with excludes**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \" Got it вҖ” **5327 means you measured a different/larger tree**, not the mirrored target we expected.\\n\\nLetвҖҷs force the exact check + clean mirror on laptop:\\n\\n```powershell\\n$src = \\\"G:\\\\My Drive\\\\openclaw-workspace-main\\\"\\n$dst = \\\"$env:USERPROFILE\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\"\\n\\n# sanity check paths\\nTest-Path $src\\nTest-Path $dst\\n\\n# clean mirror (exact)\\nrobocopy $src $dst /MIR /R:1 /W:1\\n\\n# exact counts\\n(Get-ChildItem $src -Recurse -Force | Measure-Object).Count\\n(Get-ChildItem $dst -Recurse -Force | Measure-Object).Count\\n```\\n\\nYou should see the **same number for src and dst** (currently should be around 25).  \\nIf you paste those last two numbers, IвҖҷll confirm immediately.\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8d94d8f148193b49a804a237d4669\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772673351298\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"so everyhing is on here? all agents and all workflow\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1772673853441\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Clarifying workspace sync limits**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \" Not fully, yet.\\n\\nWhatвҖҷs definitely synced:\\n- **Workspace folder** (`C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace`) via Drive.\\n\\nWhat is **not guaranteed synced** by that:\\n- all agent state\\n- session history/transcripts\\n- full `.openclaw` runtime data/workflows outside `workspace`\\n\\nSo if you mean **вҖңeverything including agents/workflows/stateвҖқ**, answer is **no, not automatically**.\\n\\nIf you want true full clone, we need to sync/copy these too:\\n- `C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\`\\n- `C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\openclaw.json`\\n- any other required `.openclaw` config/state paths\\n\\nIf you want, IвҖҷll give you one safe вҖңfull profile mirrorвҖқ command set next.\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8db41cd4c8193b81145279fa25979\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772673853445\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"вҖңfull profile mirror i want to get everything working tonight\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1772673893209\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Providing safe backup steps**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \" Yes вҖ” letвҖҷs do a **full profile mirror** tonight.\\n\\n## Plan (safe + complete)\\n\\nWeвҖҷll mirror from **desktop (main/source)** to **laptop (target)** for the whole OpenClaw profile:\\n\\n- `C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace`\\n- `C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents`\\n- `C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\openclaw.json`\\n- (optional) other `.openclaw` files\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 1) On desktop (source) вҖ” stage backup into Google Drive\\n\\nRun:\\n\\n```powershell\\n$src = \\\"$env:USERPROFILE\\\\.openclaw\\\"\\n$dst = \\\"G:\\\\My Drive\\\\openclaw-full-main\\\"\\n\\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $dst -Force | Out-Null\\n\\n# Mirror full profile, but skip noisy/lock/temp files\\nrobocopy $src $dst /MIR /R:1 /W:1 `\\n  /XD \\\"node_modules\\\" \\\".cache\\\" \\\"tmp\\\" `\\n  /XF \\\"*.lock\\\" \\\"*.tmp\\\"\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 2) On laptop (target) вҖ” stop OpenClaw first\\n\\n```powershell\\nopenclaw gateway stop\\n```\\n\\n(If needed, also close terminals/apps using OpenClaw.)\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 3) On laptop вҖ” pull full profile from Drive\\n\\n```powershell\\n$src = \\\"G:\\\\My Drive\\\\openclaw-full-main\\\"\\n$dst = \\\"$env:USERPROFILE\\\\.openclaw\\\"\\n\\nTest-Path $src\\nTest-Path $dst\\n\\nrobocopy $src $dst /MIR /R:1 /W:1 `\\n  /XD \\\"node_modules\\\" \\\".cache\\\" \\\"tmp\\\" `\\n  /XF \\\"*.lock\\\" \\\"*.tmp\\\"\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 4) On laptop вҖ” restart + verify\\n\\n```powershell\\nopenclaw gateway start --force\\nopenclaw status --deep\\nopenclaw devices list\\n```\\n\\nYou want:\\n- Gateway reachable\\n- Telegram ON/OK (if token/env present there)\\n- Devices listed\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 5) Final parity check (both machines)\\n\\nRun on both:\\n\\n```powershell\\n(Get-ChildItem \\\"$env:USERPROFILE\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\" -Recurse -Force | Measure-Object).Count\\n(Get-ChildItem \\\"$env:USERPROFILE\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\" -Recurse -Force | Measure-Object).Count\\n```\\n\\nCounts should be very close/match (excluding lock/temp files).\\n\\n---\\n\\nIf you want, I can stay with you turn-by-turn and validate each output as you run it.\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8db6e0adc819394a055ec000d2e14\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772673893217\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"run this on main\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1772673918681\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Executing main command without commit**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_Uh95Tos6fAyAPZ8U0OGLetvY|fc_016894fb01b951d60169a8db8314008193b37524f888bb43ef\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"$src = \\\"$env:USERPROFILE\\\\.openclaw\\\"; $dst = \\\"G:\\\\My Drive\\\\openclaw-full-main\\\"; New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $dst -Force | Out-Null; robocopy $src $dst /MIR /R:1 /W:1 /XD \\\"node_modules\\\" \\\".cache\\\" \\\"tmp\\\" /XF \\\"*.lock\\\" \\\"*.tmp\\\"\",\n            \"workdir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\",\n            \"yieldMs\": 120000\n          },\n          \"partialJson\": \"{\\\"command\\\":\\\"$src = \\\\\\\"$env:USERPROFILE\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\"; $dst = \\\\\\\"G:\\\\\\\\My Drive\\\\\\\\openclaw-full-main\\\\\\\"; New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $dst -Force | Out-Null; robocopy $src $dst /MIR /R:1 /W:1 /XD \\\\\\\"node_modules\\\\\\\" \\\\\\\".cache\\\\\\\" \\\\\\\"tmp\\\\\\\" /XF \\\\\\\"*.lock\\\\\\\" \\\\\\\"*.tmp\\\\\\\"\\\",\\\"workdir\\\":\\\"C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\tonyb\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\\workspace\\\",\\\"yieldMs\\\":120000}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772673918685\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Confirming robocopy success and next step**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \" Done вҖ” I ran it on main.\\n\\nFull `.openclaw` profile was mirrored to:\\n\\n- `G:\\\\My Drive\\\\openclaw-full-main`\\n\\nIt copied successfully (including agents, config, sessions, workspace, and the large backup zip).\\n\\nNext step is laptop pull. On laptop run:\\n\\n```powershell\\nopenclaw gateway stop\\n$src = \\\"G:\\\\My Drive\\\\openclaw-full-main\\\"\\n$dst = \\\"$env:USERPROFILE\\\\.openclaw\\\"\\nrobocopy $src $dst /MIR /R:1 /W:1 /XD \\\"node_modules\\\" \\\".cache\\\" \\\"tmp\\\" /XF \\\"*.lock\\\" \\\"*.tmp\\\"\\nopenclaw gateway start --force\\nopenclaw status --deep\\n```\\n\\nSend me that output and IвҖҷll verify youвҖҷre fully synced tonight.\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8db8f640881939c538df0a63bf9b6\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772673932978\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"ok i'll do that\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1772674136033\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \" Perfect. Run it on laptop and paste the `openclaw status --deep` output when done вҖ” IвҖҷll confirm final state.\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8dc5a26488193bd53b3dd7a194021\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772674136039\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"ok hopefully its woking do we have our schedule tonight\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1772674197353\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Running memory search for schedule**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_9J7JEefPZ8dMFbTL72yxXir7|fc_016894fb01b951d60169a8dc9a6590819389d83b101d9903a8\",\n          \"name\": \"memory_search\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"query\": \"tonight schedule plans events appointments\"\n          },\n          \"partialJson\": \"{\\\"query\\\":\\\"tonight schedule plans events appointments\\\"}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772674197357\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Clarifying no schedule response**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \" I checked memory and I donвҖҷt have any schedule items saved for tonight.\\n\\nIf you want, tell me what вҖңtonightвҖқ should include (or where you track it), and IвҖҷll set a clean checklist right now.\",\n          \"textSignature\": \"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8dc9fa0948193be1d47f21b5b11ae\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772674205139\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"i need you to pull all memory and everyting we've ever talked about\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1772674234845\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"**Planning comprehensive memory retrieval**\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_lez3B4EgjHUvZTif61hOydi1|fc_016894fb01b951d60169a8dcbf62a48193be211b913a2b4930\",\n          \"name\": \"memory_search\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"query\": \"all prior conversations, history, memory, decisions, preferences, todos, timeline\",\n            \"maxResults\": 50\n          },\n          \"partialJson\": \"{\\\"query\\\":\\\"all prior conversations, history, memory, decisions, preferences, todos, timeline\\\",\\\"maxResults\\\":50}\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_YiBppE3ggZXgzxEp8a94VUxh|fc_016894fb01b951d60169a8dcbf62b08193a17d34bfa283c307\",\n          \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"limit\": 50,\n            \"messageLimit\": 1\n          },\n          \"partialJson\": \"{\\\"limit\\\":50,\\\"messageLimit\\\":1}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-cod