t means Google Drive is still missing one item compared to local source.\n- Since your **laptop is offline**, it canвҖҷt receive updates anyway right now.\n\n### Telegram status\nI checked live status just now:\n- **Telegram channel = ON / OK**\n- Bot auth is healthy on this desktop\n\nSo Telegram isnвҖҷt down globally.  \nIf itвҖҷs вҖңfailing,вҖқ itвҖҷs likely one of these:\n1. YouвҖҷre testing in a **group** (your config is `groupPolicy: allowlist`, so groups are blocked unless allowed)\n2. Message routing delay or wrong chat/thread\n3. Temporary client-side issue\n\nYour current Telegram config:\n- DMs: `open` вң…\n- Groups: `allowlist` (restricted) вҡ пёҸ\n\nIf you tell me **where** itвҖҷs failing (DM vs group), IвҖҷll fix that exact path immediately.","textSignature":"msg_016894fb01b951d60169a8d32d9f7c8193b19251c906e811d3"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772671778764},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"can we get finishe"}],"timestamp":1772671870194},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Preparing sync status check**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ETz2JIDDmQrQ4ZxPwshSLnPy|fc_016894fb01b951d60169a8d38f04c881938fca845eb9903d72","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Write-Output 'SRC'; Get-ChildItem C:\\Users\\tonyb\\.openclaw\\workspace -Recurse -Force | Measure-Object; Write-Output 'DRIVE'; Get-ChildItem \"G:\\My Drive\\openclaw-workspace-main\" -Recurse -Force | Measure-Object","workdir":"C:\\Users\\tonyb\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"Write-Output 'SRC'; Get-ChildItem C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace -Recurse -Force | Measure-Object; Write-Output 'DRIVE'; Get-ChildItem \\\"G:\\\\My Drive\\\\openclaw-workspace-main\\\" -Recurse -Force | Measure-Object\",\"workdir\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\tonyb\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","st